    fixed by the Credential Management contract (the only lock); <strong>Provider</strong> = resolved behind
    the swappable credential provider, never in the surface; <strong>Member</strong> = owned by a lifecycle
    member; <strong>Compose</strong> = deferred to a neighbouring Web Everything standard.
  </p>
